    "description": "Stealth Landscaping LLC is a locally owned landscaping company based in Black Diamond, Washington, serving residential and light commercial clients throughout King County and surrounding areas. Our team of skilled landscapers is dedicated to transforming outdoor spaces into stunning landscapes through custom designs that enhance both the beauty and functionality of every property. We specialize in creating, improving, and maintaining outdoor spaces with a focus on practical, clean, and visually appealing landscape solutions tailored to each property's specific needs.\n\nWe offer a comprehensive range of services including lawn care and regular yard maintenance, seasonal cleanups, sod and turf installation (including artificial turf), shrub and tree trimming, and general landscape upkeep. Beyond maintenance, we also handle small to mid-sized landscape construction projects such as patios, retaining walls, basic hardscaping, and drainage improvements. What sets us apart is our hands-on approach with direct communication between clients and the contractor, allowing for more personalized service, attention to detail, reliable scheduling, and efficient project completion. At Stealth Landscaping, we bring your landscaping vision to life with precision and care, focusing on customized solutions rather than one-size-fits-all approaches to help you achieve improved curb appeal, healthy outdoor environments, and functional outdoor living spaces.",
